React JS Introduction: 2024
>React is a javascript library for creating ser interfaces.
> [library : predefined code]
>A user interface is the point of interface between users and a computer systems including elements like buttons ,menus, and visual layouts that facilitate navigation and control.
>>Its commonly used to build single page application
